section: ghc-lib
synopsis: Move ``NamespaceSpecifier`` from extension fields into the AST proper
issues: #26678
mrs: !15858

description: {
Move the declaration of ``NamespaceSpecifier`` from ``GHC.Hs.Basic`` to
``Language.Haskell.Syntax.ImpExp`` and parameterise it by the compiler pass,
creating the necessary extension points. Update ``FixitySig``, ``IEThingAll``,
and ``IEWholeNamespace`` to store ``NamespaceSpecifier`` directly rather than
in their extension fields.
}
